data.description: Nestled on a rural, countryside .5-acre lot, this inviting completely remodeled 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, oversize 2 car garage block home offers spacious living and luxury finishes. The interior boasts over 1,600 sq. ft. of living space with an amazing formal dining setting, an eat-in kitchen, and a magnificent family room. The Chef in the family will love the 42-inch, Custom-Crafted Kitchen Cabinets. Pearl White Granite countertops with a polished beveled edge & white tiled backsplash. The large owners suite boast double closets. beautiful grey vinyl floors flow throughout the houses except bedrooms where carpet and pad have been installed. Roof is only 2 years old and A/C is 1 year old. No CDD or HOA! Easy access to I-4, HWY 60, Tampa and Orlando shopping and dining.
